quran[99]{c,v,t}:
  15,1,"A L R , those are The Book`s evidences/verses , and (an) evident/clear Koran"
  15,2,Maybe those who disbelieved wish/love if they were Moslems/submitters/surrenderers
  15,3,"Leave them eat and they live long/enjoy, and the hope distracts/preoccupies them , so they will/shall know"
  15,4,"And We did not destroy from a village/urban city , except and for it (is) a known Book"
  15,5,"None from a nation precedes its term/time, and they do not delay (it)"
  15,6,"And they said: \"You, you who the reminder/remembrance was descended on him, that you are mad/insane (E)"
  15,7,"If you (could) come to us with the angels , if you were from truthful! (expression of wonderment)"
  15,8,"We do not descend the angels except with the truth , and they (the disbelievers) were not then delayed/waited"
  15,9,"That We, We descended the reminder/remembrance, and that We (are) for it, protectors/guards (E)"
  15,10,And We had descended from before you in the first`s/beginner`s groups/parties
  15,11,"And none from a messenger comes to them , except they were with him mocking/making fun"
  15,12,As/like that We enter/insert it in the criminals`/sinners` hearts/minds
  15,13,"They do not believe with it, and (the) manner/nature (of) the firsts/beginners had past/expired"
  15,14,"And if We opened on them a door/entrance from the sky/space, so they continued/remained in it ascending/zigzagging"
  15,15,"They would have said: \"But our eye/sights/understanding got closed and confused, but we are a bewitched/enchanted nation"
  15,16,"And We had made/created in the sky/space constellations, and We decorated/beautified it to the lookers/seers"
  15,17,And We protected/guarded it from every cursed/expelled devil
  15,18,"Except who eavesdropped the hearing, so a clear/evident light from a fire source/a star followed him"
  15,19,"And the earth/Planet Earth, We extended/spread it, and We threw in it anchors/mountains , and We sprouted/grew in it from every thing weighed/measured/balanced"
  15,20,"And We made/created for you in it livelihoods/sustenances, and whom you are not to him with providing for"
  15,21,"And that (there is not) from a thing, except at Us (is) its safes (treasures) , and We do not descent it except with (a) known measure/quantity"
  15,22,"And We sent the winds/breezes (as) pollinators , so We descended from the sky water, so We gave it to you to drink, and you are not for it with storing"
  15,23,"And that We, We are (E), We revive/make life and We make die, and We are the heirs/inheritants"
  15,24,"And We had known the advanced from you, and We had known the delayed/lagging behind"
  15,25,"And that your Lord, He gathers them, that He is wise/judicious, knowledgeable"
  15,26,And We had created the human/mankind from black (foul mud) dry mud/clay smoothened/rotted
  15,27,"And the Jinn , We created him from before from (the) fire`s burning wind"
  15,28,"When/if your Lord said to the angels : \"That I am creating (a) human/humans from black (foul mud) dry mud/clay smoothened/rotted"
  15,29,"So when/if I straightened him, and I blew in him from My Soul/Sprit , so fall/land/come to him prostrating"
  15,30,So the angels all/all together prostrated
  15,31,"Except Satan/Iblis , refused/hated that he be with the prostrating"
  15,32,"He said: \"You Satan , why (is it) for you (that) you not be with the prostrating"
  15,33,"He said: \"I was not to prostrate to (a) human You created him from black (foul mud) from dry mud/clay smoothened/rotted"
  15,34,"He said: \"So get out from it, so that you are cursed/expelled"
  15,35,And that on you (is) the curse/torture to the Judgment`s Day/Resurrection Day
  15,36,"He said: \"My Lord, so delay me to a day they be sent/resurrected/revived"
  15,37,"He said: \"So that (then) you are from the delayed"
  15,38,"To (the) day of the time, the known"
  15,39,"He said: \"My Lord with what You misguided/enticed me , I will decorate/beautify for them in the earth/Planet Earth, and I will misguide/entice them (E) all/all together"
  15,40,"Except Your worshippers/slaves from them, the faithful/loyal/devoted"
  15,41,"He said: \"That (is) a straight/direct road/way on Me"
  15,42,"That My worshippers/slaves, power/control is not for you on them (you have no power/control over My worshippers/slaves) except who followed you from the misguided/failed"
  15,43,And that Hell (is) their appointment (E) all/all together
  15,44,"For it (are) seven doors/entrances, to each door/entrance from them (is an) apportioned/divided part/portion"
  15,45,That the fearing and obeying (are) in treed gardens/paradises and water springs/wells
  15,46,"Enter it with safety/security/peace, safe/secure"
  15,47,"And We removed/pulled away what (is) in their chests (innermosts) from hatred/animosity , brothers on beds/sofas facing each other"
  15,48,"Hardship/fatigue does not touch them in it, and they are not with being brought out from it"
  15,49,"Inform My worshippers/slaves, that I, I am the forgiving , the merciful"
  15,50,"And that My torture, it is the torture, the painful"
  15,51,And inform them about Abraham`s guests
  15,52,"When/if they entered on (to) him, so they said: \"Greeting/peace .\" He said: \"That we are afraid/apprehensive from you"
  15,53,"They said: \"Do not be afraid/apprehensive, that we, we announce good news to you with (of) a knowledgeable boy (new son)"
  15,54,"He said: \"Did you announce good news to me on that the old age touched me so with what (do) you announce177good news to me"
  15,55,"They said: \"We announced to you with the good news, so do not be from the despaired/despairing"
  15,56,"He said: \"And who despairs from his Lord`s mercy, except the misguided"
  15,57,"He said: \"So what (is) your matter/affair/concern, you, the messengers"
  15,58,"They said: \"We are sent to a nation (of) criminals/sinners"
  15,59,"Except Lot`s family, We are saving/rescuing them (E) all together"
  15,60,Except his woman (wife). We predestined/evaluated that she truly is from (E) the remaining behind
  15,61,So when the messengers came (to) Lot`s family
  15,62,"He said: \"That you are a disguised/unknown nation"
  15,63,"They said: \"But we came to you, with what they were in it doubting/arguing"
  15,64,"And we came/brought (to) you with the truth , and that we are truthful (E)"
  15,65,"So move/travel/depart at night with your family/people with portions from the night and follow their backs/ends; and no one from you (should) turn around , and proceed/complete where/when you are being ordered/commanded"
  15,66,"And We ordered/passed judgment to him (of) that the matter/affair/order/command, that those (people`s) root/remainder (is) cut off/severed by the morning/daybreak"
  15,67,And the city`s/town`s people came cheerful/rejoicing
  15,68,"He said: \"That those (are) my guests, so do not expose my faults (scandalize me)"
  15,69,And fear and obey God and do not shame/disgrace me
  15,70,"They said: \"And did we not forbid/prevent you from the creations all together/(universes)"
  15,71,"He said: \"Those (are) my daughters, if you were making/doing"
  15,72,To your life/age (an oath) that they truly are in (E) their intoxication/loss of judgment being confused/puzzled
  15,73,So the loud strong cry/torture raid took/punished them at sunrise
  15,74,"So We made its highest/elevated , its lowest/bottom, and We rained on them stones of dry and hardened mud"
  15,75,"That in that (are) evidences/signs (E) , to the observing/scrutinizing"
  15,76,And that it truly is with a continuing/keeping up path/means (E)
  15,77,That in that (is) a sign/evidence (E) to the believers
  15,78,And if owners/company (of) the thicket/dense tangled trees were unjust/oppressive (E)
  15,79,So We revenged from them that they (B) truly (the two nations) are with a clear/evident leader/example (E)
  15,80,And the forbidden`s/mind`s owners/company denied the messengers
  15,81,"And We gave/brought them Our verses/evidences , so they were objecting/opposing/turning away from it"
  15,82,And they were carving out/cutting from the mountains houses/homes safely/securely
  15,83,So the loud strong cry/torture raid took/punished them in the morning/daybreak
  15,84,So what they were gaining/acquiring did not enrich/suffice them from them (was of no benefit to them)
  15,85,"And We did not create the skies/space and the earth/Planet Earth and what (is) between them (B) except with the truth , and that truly the Hour/Resurrection is coming (E) so forgive/pardon the forgiveness/pardon, the beautiful/graceful"
  15,86,"That truly your Lord (is) the creator (E), the knowledgeable"
  15,87,"And We had given/brought you seven from the doubles/strength/capacity and the Koran , the great"
  15,88,"Do not extend/spread your two eyes to what We made spouses/couples from them enjoy with it, and do not be sad/grievous on (for) them, and be lenient/comforting/lower your wing/side (kindness) to the believers"
  15,89,"And say: \"That I, I am the warner/giver of notice, the clear/evident"
  15,90,As We descended on the apportioners/dividers/distributors
  15,91,Those who made the Koran bits/divisions/enchantments
  15,92,"So by/with your Lord, We will ask/question them (E) all together"
  15,93,About what they were making/doing
  15,94,"So uncover/declare openly with what you are being ordered/commanded, and turn away from the sharers/takers of partners (with God)"
  15,95,That We truly make you sufficient (protect you) against the mocking/making fun
  15,96,"Those who create/put with God another god, so they will/shall know"
  15,97,"And We had know (known) that you, your chest (innermost) narrows/tightens becuase (of) what they say"
  15,98,"So praise/glorify with your Lord`s praise/gratitude/thanks, and be from the prostrating"
  15,99,"And worship your Lord, until the assurance/certainty (death) comes to you"